    <body>
        
        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>Down</placeName>
                    <date>Friday night.</date>
                    <salute>My dear Hooker</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>The very sight of your handwriting always does me good.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/> You poor miserable wretch you must groan when you see mine, for I think I have always some request. Do not return medallion of D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. Darwin, but keep it till you come here on our return—<ref target="#foot.f3"/> I start next Wednesday or Thursday; perhaps staying in London for a day to see Busk if there.<ref target="#foot.f4"/> From what Goodsir said I had already written to consult Busk.<ref target="#foot.f5"/> but was glad to be confirmed by your advice.<ref target="#foot.f6"/> </p>
<p>About New Zealand, at last I am coming round &amp; admit it must have been connected with some Terra firma; but I will die rather than admit Australia.<ref target="#foot.f7"/> How I wish mountains of New Caledonia were well worked.—</p>
<p>Never mind about New Zealand map.—<ref target="#foot.f8"/></p>
<p>I think you will enjoy a tour in the great gardens: I was speechless with admiration, years ago, at Chatsworth.—<ref target="#foot.f9"/></p>
<p>I have only one request (wonderful moderation): will cuttings strike, or can suckers be separated of a palm (Calamus??) with shoots ending in hooks.<ref target="#foot.f10"/> If possible, on my return in 5 or 6 weeks I sh<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. very much like a young plant, <hi rend="underline">with growing internodes</hi>, to look for movements.—<ref target="#foot.f11"/> Probably this is not possible. Ask Hugh Gower.—<ref target="#foot.f12"/></p>
<p>Goodnight | Your troublesome old friend | C. D.</p>
<p>I am very sorry to hear about Miss Henslow.—<ref target="#foot.f13"/></p> 
                </div>
            </div>
                <div type="tnotes">
